 <sect1>
  <title>Boot Loader Configuration</title>

  <para>
   After the upgrade of &dom0;, &xen; is no longer selected as the default
   boot option in the grub boot menu. To make it default, start &yast; and
   select <menuchoice><guimenu>System</guimenu> <guimenu>Boot Loader</guimenu>
   <guimenu>Boot Loader Options</guimenu></menuchoice>. Then select the
   <systemitem>XEN</systemitem> entry in <guimenu>Default Boot
   Section</guimenu>. Finish with <guimenu>OK</guimenu>.
  </para>
 </sect1>
